<html><head><title>Guild Recruitment Festival</title></head><body class="newsbody" ><div class=newbody><h2>EverQuest Vault -- EQ </h3><h3>Guild Recruitment Festival</h3><p>With the influx of people coming back to the game this month, guilds will be opening their ranks for people looking to join.<br><br>SOE is making it easier with the guild recruitment festival:<br><br>Are you new to Norrath? Are you returning after a long vacation and looking to join a guild? Are you an old timer that finally decided to take the big plunge? Or perhaps you are a guild leader looking to recruit new members to your guild? Then join us for the Norrathian Guild Recruitment Festival! <br><br>From June 18th through July 25th, EverQuest will be hosting the Norrathian Guild Recruitment Festival. The festival will begin website news articles listing guilds that are recruiting. Throughout the period in-game social events will occur so keep your eyes peeled.<br><br>Come meet up with fellow adventurers across the world of Norrath and beyond. Converse with the community and learn about the guilds on your server and what they are looking for in prospective applicants. <br><br>SOE has an official <a href="http://forums.station.sony.com/eq/posts/list.m?topic_id=133882">guild recruiting page</a> where you can post or find a guild looking for members.<br></div><p><div classs=copyright><font face=arial size=2 color=#959595>News Story from EverQuest Vault -- EQ <br>News Date: Thursday, 19 Jun, 2008<br>Link: <a href="http://eqvault.ign.com/fullstory.php?id=42460">http://eqvault.ign.com/fullstory.php?id=42460</a><br>Printed On: Sat Aug 25 10:02:51 PDT 2012<br>©2008 IGN Entertainment</font></span>